Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:46.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鮮烈過ぎた年回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏見のあるカテゴライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:50.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Don't believe no story
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:52.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I know you're ready
