Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:07.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:12.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这定罪的把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:14.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇异的独角戏舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:17.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看着 竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:22.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遗落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:22.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺骗吧 Close Enough
