Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}许下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得赞美的惊恐
