Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}带有偏见的分类
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:50.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:52.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你准备好了
